'''Raava''' was a [[Socorro/Legends|Socorran]] [[Alcohol/Legends|liquor]] made from the concentrated extract of [[Zsajhira berry|zsajhira berries]] and water from Socorro's neighboring planet, [[Neftali/Legends|Neftali]]. [[Ethra Brewery]] had a monopoly on the production of raava, which it sold in black bottles made from the planet's well-known black sands.<ref name="BSS" />

[[Drake Paulsen]] was both known to enjoy raava.<ref name="idol">{{JournalCite|12|Idol Intentions}}</ref>

